      "description": "This vehicle is in impeccable, mint condition and presents exactly as it did on the showroom floor. The exterior finish is absolutely flawless with a mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has been kept in a climate-controlled environment with a complete service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly like-new example of this model.",
